main event: Observers in Franklin, Texas reported two unidentified objects slowly moving southward for over six hours on 18 September 1965.
interesting points: The objects appeared to be very distant and travelled at a high rate of speed., The objects faded in and out and appeared in three different locations simultaneously., Observers described the objects as shimmering and fluctuating in brightness., The conclusion leaned towards identifying the objects as astronomical phenomena., A subsequent UFO observation in 1966 referred to similar behaviors of unidentified objects.
